--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 Spells<br>
------<br>
- All pets will now zone with their master.<br>
- Given Paladins Complete Heal at level 55.<br>
- Spectral Parchments now drop in tier 1 and more readily in tier 2 planes.<br>
- New Tanann is now rumored to be selling lost scrolls obtained from Kunark, Velious, and Luclin.<br>
- Casters above level 55 may now cast on the run.<br>
- Root and Charm line spells are no longer random duration spells.<br>
- Root spells will no longer break when a Direct Damage spell is cast on the mob.<br>
- Slow line of spells were generating too much agro. This has been fixed.<br>
- When a mob it rooted and feared it will no longer act as if it were not feared.<br>
<br>
Zones<br>
------<br>
- Removed the need to be Flagged in order to enter Planes of Power zones.<br>
<br>
Class<br>
------<br>
- Lay on Hands and Harm Touch reuse times have been reduced to 36 minutes instead of its previous 72.<br>
- Harm Touch has the chance to kill a mob outright for Shadow Knights 50+<br>
- Rangers will get Double bow damage from level 1.<br>
- Rogues have the chance to kill a mob outright with a thrown dagger.<br>
- Mend Companion is now an innate ability for Mages and Necromancers.<br>
<br>
Altnernate Advancement<br>
-----------------------<br>
- Added Feign Death to General AA. Monks who purchase this AA will find the reuse on the skill lowered per rank.<br>
<br>
